com.cyc.kb

Interface FirstOrderCollection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KbCollection, KbObject, KbObject.KbObjectWithArity, KbTerm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FirstOrderCollectionWrapper

    public interface FirstOrderCollection
extends KbCollection
    The interface for KbCollections whose members are all KbIndividuals. In other words, no FirstOrderCollection contains a KbCollection.

      • getGeneralizations

        Collection<FirstOrderCollection> getGeneralizations()
        Finds the asserted generalizations of this KbCollection, from the default context specified by DefaultContext.forQuery(). The only difference is that it is known that any generalization of FirstOrderCollection is itself a FirstOrderCollection.
        Specified by:
        getGeneralizations in interface KbCollection
        Returns:
        the KbCollections that are generalizations of this KbCollection

      • getGeneralizations

        Collection<FirstOrderCollection> getGeneralizations(Context ctx)
